msgstr "consciousness—which is a killer—as a killer."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.85:21.1"
msgid "So rūpaṃ upeti upādiyati adhiṭṭhāti ‘attā me’ti."
msgstr ""
"They’re attracted to form, grasp it, and commit to the notion that it is ‘my "
"self’."

msgctxt "sn22.85:21.2"
msgid "Vedanaṃ …"
msgstr "They’re attracted to feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:21.3"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:21.4"
msgid "saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:21.5"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ upeti upādiyati adhiṭṭhāti ‘attā me’ti."
msgstr "consciousness, grasp it, and commit to the notion that it is ‘my self’."

msgctxt "sn22.85:21.6"
msgid ""
"Tassime pañcupādānakkhandhā upetā upādinnā dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"And when you’ve gotten involved with and grasped these five grasping "
"aggregates, they lead to your lasting harm and suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.85:22.1"
msgid ""
"Sutavā ca kho, āvuso, ariyasāvako ariyānaṃ dassāvī … pe … sappurisadhamme "
"suvinīto "
msgstr ""
"An educated noble disciple has seen the noble ones, and is skilled and "
"trained in the teaching of the noble ones. They’ve seen good persons, and "
"are skilled and trained in the teaching of the good persons. "

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.2"
msgid ""
"na rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ attānaṃ; na attani rūpaṃ, na "
"rūpasmiṃ attānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They don’t regard form as self, self as having form, form in self, or self "
"in form."

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.3"
msgid "Na vedanaṃ …"
msgstr "They don’t regard feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.4"
msgid "na saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.5"
msgid "na saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.6"
msgid "na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ attānaṃ;"
msgstr "consciousness as self, self as having consciousness,"

msgctxt "sn22.85:22.7"
msgid "na attani viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ attānaṃ."
msgstr "consciousness in self, or self in consciousness."

